      "content": "<p>Each of the three sponges was inhabited by at least one male <em><span data-ssml-sub-alias=\"A\">A.</span> fasciatus</em> and at least one undetermined <em><span data-ssml-sub-alias=\"A\">A.</span> fasciatus</em>.</p>"
    },
