    {
      "id": "3d3630b6-2a6b-408b-80d9-71e92a3a4b1a",
      "content": "<p>Each of the three sponges was inhabited by at least one male <em><span data-ssml-sub-alias=\"A\">A.</span> fasciatus</em> and at least one female <em>A. fasciatus</em>.</p>"
    },
